{"id":"2126eace-afcc-47a2-a65d-eae5438b7942","name":"Dominic Becker","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">◇ — <strong>Firehouse 62 </strong>— <strong>◇</strong><br><strong> </strong>oc | modern setting | tough leader</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_65d77937-a61a-43fa-b111-f328bd9a8d01.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><em><span style=\"color: rgba(183, 148, 244, 0.725)\">You were recently approved as a candidate for Firehouse 62, but even if you're efficient, productive or proactive, there's nothing stopping Becker from picking on you.</span></em></p><p><em><span style=\"color: rgba(183, 148, 244, 0.725)\">Becker doesn't care if he's destroying your dreams of becoming a firefighter, he doesn't care about your fucking feelings... he can't lose anyone else because of carelessness on shift.</span></em></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 632px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_2c069dee-d376-4c12-ad64-ece47d7c7ae7.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">First of all... OMG <strong>165</strong> followers, THANK YOU SO MUCH!!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\">I've had the idea for this series for a long time, and I finally decided to do it. </span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\">Each character in the series will be involved with the </span><em><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\">user</span></em><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\"> in a different way, </span><em><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\">user</span></em><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\"> will not necessarily be a firefighter or something like that in every scenario.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\">Remember that I </span>LOVE <span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\">receiving suggestions from you, so if you have any, please comment as it will help a lot in creating the next bots.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 190px; height: 114.357px; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_f7fa9cc3-515e-4c72-b1b1-6491681e1642.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 644px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_ee2e4e5b-4c2b-4b15-bd78-e6b51ac08eac.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">This is the </span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">first</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> bot of the </span><strong>Firehouse 62</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> series</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 121, 192)\">This series will be based on the fictional Firehouse 62, involving characters of firefighters, rescue personnel, and paramedics, and all the drama that surrounds their lives.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 121, 192)\">After all, who wouldn't want to be rescued by a hot firefighter?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_0c18f997-0135-4a0b-92e4-feac708dc86a.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e1a42719-1ce7-472f-95e9-618a837e678f_character-noah-o-sullivan-sully\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Noah O'Sullivan (Sully)<span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\"> </span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\">— </span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\">◇ </span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(201, 180, 255)\">—</span> <a ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"43978859-0367-4944-9a8c-1dab5fa7418a_abdfb8e8-7b5f-414f-a74c-ae6988b9b4ba.webp","creator":"chloehills","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers"],"chats":1056,"messages":46273,"created_at":"2024-06-27T15:33:16.693737+00:00"}